42  void SelectionOrderCriteria::execute(Dvector& Parcor) {
43 
44  mEps(0) = Parcor(0);
46  double parsum = 0.0;
47 
48 
49  for (unsigned int k = 1; k < mMaxOrder; k++) {
50  mEps(k) = (1 - Parcor(k) * Parcor(k)) * mEps(k - 1);
51 
52  parsum = 0.0;
53  for (unsigned int j = 1; j < k; j++)
54  parsum += (mN - j) / (mN * mEps(j));
55 
56  mFpe(k) = mEps(k)*(mN + k + 1.0) / (mN - k - 1.0);
57  mMdl(k) = log(mEps(k)) + k * log(mN) / mN;
58  mAic(k) = log(mEps(k)) + 2.0 * k / mN;
59  mCat(k) = (1.0 / mN) * parsum - (mN - k) / (mN * mEps(k));
60 
61  mHQ(k) = log(mEps(k)) + 2 * k * log(log(mN)) / mN;
62  mAicC(k) = log(mEps(k)) + 2 * (k + 1) / (mN - k - 2);
63 
64  double parprod = 1.0;
65  for (unsigned int j = 1; j < k; j++)
66  parprod *= (1 + 1 / (mN + 1 - j)) / (1 - 1 / (mN + 1 - j));
67 
68  mFsic(k) = log(mEps(k)) + parprod - 1;
69  mCic(k) = mFsic(k) + k;
70  }
71  mFpe(0) = mFpe(1);
72  mMdl(0) = mMdl(1);
73  mAic(0) = mAic(1);
74  mCat(0) = mCat(1);
75 
76  mHQ(0) = mHQ(1);
77  mAicC(0) = mAicC(1);
78  mFsic(0) = mFsic(1);
79  mCic(0) = mCic(1);
80 
81  }
82 
83 }
